<p>The Alexandria University Cancer Research Cluster (CERC) is the first ‚Äúprototype‚Äù research cluster in Egypt. It was conceptualized to transfer the operational model of an international research organization to Alexandria University, in terms of its scientific and administrative structure, as well as its operating procedures.</p>

